  Use-Cases :
      1. Auth :
        ✔ a. User Registers : @done(25-02-07 13:53)
          ✔ Validate User Input @done(25-02-07 13:50)
          ✔ Hash password using bcrypt @done(25-02-07 13:50)
          ✔ Save User to DB @done(25-02-07 13:50)
          

        b. User Logs In :
          ✔ Validate User Input @done(25-02-07 13:51) @today
          ✔ Check if User exists @done(25-02-07 13:51)
          ✔ Check if password is correct @high @done(25-02-07 14:24)
          ✔ Generate JWT @low @started(25-02-07 14:24) @done(25-02-07 16:47) @lasted(2h23m22s)
          ✔ Send JWT to client @done(25-02-07 16:47)
      
      2. User:

          a. User Logs Out :
            - Delete JWT from client

          b. User Updates Profile :
            - Validate User Input
            - Check if User exists
            - Update User in DB
          
          c. User Deletes Profile :
            - Check if User exists
            - Delete User from DB

      3. Notes :

        a. User Creates A Note :
          - Authenticate User using JWT
          - Validate User Input
          - Save Note to DB

        b. User Updates A Note :
          - Authenticate User using JWT
          - Validate User Input
          - Check if Note exists
          - Update Note in DB

        c. User Deletes A Note :
          - Authenticate User using JWT
          - Check if Note exists
          - Delete Note from DB

        d. User Views A Note :
          - Authenticate User using JWT
          - Check if Note exists
          - Return Note to User

        e. User Views All Notes :
          - Return All Notes to User 

      


     
        



